class=\"lead\">At nearly one and half meters wide, the impressive 4-oven AGA Cooker is bursting with must-have features. As well as the roasting, slow cook and baking ovens of the 3-oven AGA Cooker, the 4-oven AGA Cooker features a warming oven.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side\"><img class=\"featurette-image img-responsive\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/4-OVEN-AGA_Black_470x332.jpg\" alt=\"AGA Traditional Cooker\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(4059,677,'_featurette_a','field_528ad8dffd9e4'),(4060,677,'featurette_b','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main-odd\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">4-Oven Electric</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">Like all AGA cookers, the 4-oven Electric AGA Cooker is made of cast-iron. It\'s this iron that radiates the heat through its ovens and hotplates, allowing it to always be instantly available for use and preventing food from drying out, while retaining goodness and enhancing natural flavors. The ambient heat it provides keeps kitchens and even adjoining rooms deliciously warm.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side-odd\"><img class=\"featurette-image img-responsive\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/4-oven-aga_Duck-Egg-Blue_470x332.jpg\" alt=\"AGA Traditional Cooker\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(4061,677,'_featurette_b','field_528ad98ffd9e5'),(4062,677,'featurette_c','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">3-Oven Gas</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">The 3-oven AGA Cooker adds a baking oven to the roasting and slow cook ovens of the 2-oven AGA Cooker, offering added versatility to your cooking.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side\"><img class=\"featurette-image img-responsive\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/AGA_white_cutout_LAYERED_470x561.jpg\" alt=\"AGA Traditional Cooker\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(4063,677,'_featurette_c','field_528adda1a27c9'),(4064,677,'featurette_d','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main-odd\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">2-Oven Gas</h2>\r\nThe 2-oven gas AGA Cooker has a boiling plate and simmering plate, plus a roasting oven and slow cook oven. These are kept constantly ready for use by the cooker\'s unique heat technology, made possible by its cast-iron body.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side-odd\"><img class=\"featurette-image img-responsive\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/AGA-2-Oven_Pearl-Ashes_470x483.jpg\" alt=\"AGA Traditional Cooker\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(4065,677,'_featurette_d','field_528add60a27c7'),(4066,677,'featurette_e','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">2-Oven Electric</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">First engineered more than 20 years ago, the 2-oven electric AGA Cooker is a great choice for those looking for real cost efficiency. The beauty of the 2-oven electric AGA Cooker is that it takes full advantage of off-peak electricity, storing it through the night in specially designed heat bricks located deep inside the cooker. The stored energy is then used to heat the AGA Cooker throughout the day, reducing running costs.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side\"><img class=\"featurette-image img-responsive\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/AGA-2-Oven_PEWTER_470x483.jpg\" alt=\"AGA Traditional Cooker\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(4067,677,'_featurette_e','field_528ae3c4694fd'),(4068,677,'featurette_f',''),(4069,677,'_featurette_f','field_528ae3e0694fe'),(4070,677,'featurette_g',''),(8285,1148,'_featurette_b','field_528ad98ffd9e5'),(8286,1148,'featurette_c','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Bake</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">The Thermashell’s natural convection with added radiant reflection produces better airflow and browning than competitive top vented grills.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image alignnone wp-image-1592 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Caliber_Thermashell_Bake.jpg\" alt=\"Caliber Thermashell Bake\" width=\"470\" height=\"350\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(4071,677,'_featurette_g','field_528ae3f6694ff'),(4072,677,'featurette_h',''),(8283,1148,'_featurette_a','field_528ad8dffd9e4'),(8284,1148,'featurette_b','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main-odd\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Smoke</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">With the Caliber Thermashell Pro™ Grill &amp; Smoker, you can relax and smoke with confidence. Set the heat for Low and Slow at 225˚ for 4, 5, or 6 hours and let our smoker do the work. Brisket fans can run the smoker on a single stock of fuel starting at 225˚ and see the temperature at 205˚ - 12 hours later!</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side-odd\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image alignnone wp-image-1591 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Caliber_Thermashell_Smoke.jpg\" alt=\"Caliber Thermashell Smoke\" width=\"470\" height=\"350\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(4073,677,'_featurette_h','field_528ae41e69500'),(4074,677,'_edit_lock','1415052073:1'),(4075,677,'kia_subtitle','Since first designed, AGA Cookers have been considered the heart of the home'),(4076,679,'_edit_last','1'),(4077,679,'_wp_page_template','page-templates/product-page-full-width-acf.php'),(4078,680,'intro_paragraph','Skate ipsum dolor sit amet, Natas Kaupas bruised heel hip invert Tracker dude crail grab. Backside Primo slide lien air nose Rector gnar bucket darkslide. 540 rip grip kickturn aerial frontside air frigid air. Pressure flip face plant spine soul skate betty wheels. Alley oop skate or die coffin grab egg plant pump. Boardslide gnarly crail grab frigid air