ange Cooker - TC3</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">The AGA Total Control Range TC3 Cooker is a newly designed version of the classic icon of British cooking. Three radiant-heat cast iron ovens and two hotplates give you 10 delicious ways to cook in one range.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side\"><img class=\"featurette-image img-responsive\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/colors_duck_egg_blue_470x460.jpg\" alt=\"AGA TC3 Total Control Cooker\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(4099,679,'_featurette_a','field_528ad8dffd9e4'),(4100,679,'featurette_b','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main-odd\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Total Control Range Cooker - TC5</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">The new TC5, the latest model in the Total Control series, brings you five large cast iron ovens, two hotplates and a warming plate to deliver incredible capacity and flexibility.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side-odd\"><img class=\"featurette-image img-responsive\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/tc5-blk-l_470x350.jpg\" alt=\"AGA TC5 Total Control Cooker\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(4101,679,'_featurette_b','field_528ad98ffd9e5'),(4102,679,'featurette_c','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Total Control Cooker Hotplates</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">AGA Total Control Cookers hotplates can do anything. They can boil, simmer, grill, stir-fry, fry and toast.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side\"><a href=\"/product/aga/total-control-cookers/picture-11045-2/#main\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-1066\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image img-responsive wp-image-1066\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/tcc_left_Plate_with_vent_324x350.jpg\" alt=\"AGA Total Control Cooker Hotplates\" /></a></div>\r\n</div>'),(4103,679,'_featurette_c','field_528adda1a27c9'),(4104,679,'featurette_d','<div class=\"row f