470\" height=\"350\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(6186,892,'intro_paragraph','Marvel brings you the widest selection of built-in refrigeration sizes and configurations, including all-refrigerators, all-freezers, refrigerator/freezers, wine cellars and beverage centers. Models are available in 6 inch increments from 18 to 72 inches. Marvel’s full-size integrated solutions are never mass produced, but made just for you with years of experience, craftsmanship, and the highest quality components.'),(6233,897,'_featurette_a','field_528ad8dffd9e4'),(6234,897,'featurette_b','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-7 content-col-main-odd\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">MARVEL 30\" Built-in All Refrigerator</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">Skate ipsum dolor sit amet, 720 bone air layback kick-nose acid drop feeble. Camel back Eric Koston hip 540 kick-nose grab bluntslide. Darkslide pressure flip slob air wall ride wax hand rail.</p>\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" role=\"button\" href=\"#\">View details »</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-5 content-col-side-odd\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image img-responsive\" alt=\"Generic placeholder image\" src=\"http://placehold.it/470x350\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(6231,897,'_intro_paragraph','field_528baacf900df'),(6232,897,'featurette_a','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-7 content-col-main\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">MARVEL 24\" Built-in All Refrigerator</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">Delete Unused Featurette on page if not needed. Skate ipsum dolor sit amet, 720 bone air layback kick-nose acid drop feeble. Camel back Eric Koston hip 540 kick-nose grab bluntslide. Darkslide pressure flip slob air wall ride wax hand rail.</p>\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" role=\"button\" href=\"#\">View details »</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-5 content-col-side\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image img-responsive alt=\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://placehold.it/470x350\" /></div>\r\n</div