nd within easy reach.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-5 content-col-side-odd\"><a href=\"/product/marvel-products/marvel-undercounter-refrigeration/marvel-professional/stacking-units/mpro-66wdm-143x350/#main\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-1041\"><img class=\"featurette-image img-responsive wp-image-1041\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/mpro-66wdm-143x350.jpg\" alt=\"Marvel Professional Wine Cellar / Refrigerated Drawer Combination Unit\" width=\"143\" height=\"350\" /></a></div>\r\n</div>'),(7126,986,'_featurette_b','field_528ad98ffd9e5'),(7127,986,'featurette_c','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-7 content-col-main\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Marvel Professional Dual Wine Cellar</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">Combine two Marvel Professional Wine Cellars for an amazing 108 bottle display. The blue LED interior lighting and temperature controls give your collection a subtle yet striking presentation. Each unit delivers accurate temperature control between 40° and 65° F, and our exclusive Vibration Neutralization System™ protects your wine from damaging vibration. Attractive and durable black finish cabinets are perfect for both free-standing or built-in use.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-5 content-col-side\"><a href=\"/product/marvel-products/marvel-undercounter-refrigeration/marvel-professional/stacking-units/mpro-66wcm-143x350/#main\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-1042\"><img class=\"featurette-image img-responsive wp-image-1042\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/mpro-66wcm-143x350.jpg\" alt=\"Marvel Professional Combination Unit\" width=\"143\" height=\"350\" /></a></div>\r\n</div>'),(7128,986,'_featurette_c','field_528adda1a27c9'),(7129,986,'featurette_d',''),(11519,1361,'_wp_page_template','page-templates/product-page-full-width-acf.php'),(11520,1361,'kia_subtitle','A home grilling experience wherever life takes you.'),(11521,1361,'_wpdh_display_header','/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/copy-1400x600textHero+Banner+Image+1400x60