 details »</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-3 col-md-3\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image img-responsive\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/heartland-btn.png\" alt=\"AGA\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-3 col-md-3\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Marvel</h2>\r\nThe best of everything comes together in Marvel undercounter refrigeration. Elegant styling, smart shelving designs, and superior performance from products built in the USA.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" title=\"Marvel Products\" href=\"/product/marvel-products/\">View details »</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-3 col-md-3\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image img-responsive\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/marvel-btn.png\" alt=\"Vent-A-Hood\" width=\"218\" height=\"260\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(10409,1305,'_plp_row_2','field_528bc40e66b80'),(10410,1305,'plp_row_3','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-3 col-md-3\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">ILVE</h2>\r\n<b>ILVE® (pronounced \"ILL-VAY\")</b> began as a brand in 1952 and has since been the epitome of hand-crafted quality in residential and commercial ovens and cooktops. The state of the art manufacturing facility, located near historic Venice, Italy represents more than 50 years of tradition, continuous technological research, and relentless innovation.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" title=\"ILVE Appliance\" href=\"/product/ilve/\">View details »</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-3 col-md-3\"><a href=\"/product/ilve-um-150_218x260_brighter/#main\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-1092\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail  alignnone wp-image-1092 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/ilve-UM-150_218x260_brighter.jpg\" alt=\"Ilve Appliances\" width=\"218\" height=\"260\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-3 col-md-3\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Verona</h2>\r\nThe stylish Verona line of ranges, ovens and cooktops are a preferred brand of appliances featured in upscale kitche