ontent-col-side\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image img-responsive alt=\" src=\"http://placehold.it/470x350\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(11867,1382,'_featurette_a','field_528ad8dffd9e4'),(11868,1382,'featurette_b','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-7 content-col-main-odd\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Oval Woodburning Cookstove</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">The original Oval has been heating homes, warming water, and cooking meals for almost a century.</p>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">Today’s models offer the same dependability, comfort, and tremendous versatility. But Heartland has incorporated some important changes to make your life easier than it was for your ancestors.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side-odd\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image img-responsive\" src=\"http://placehold.it/470x350\" alt=\"Generic placeholder image\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(11869,1382,'_featurette_b','field_528ad98ffd9e5'),(11870,1382,'featurette_c','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Artisan Woodburning Cookstove</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">The Artisan wood burning cookstove is unlike any other woodstove. Its gentle, radiant heat is transferred through the internal cast iron structure, spreading the heat evenly to the ovens and hotplate. By bathing food in heat from all directions, flavors are sealed in without drying.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image img-responsive\" src=\"http://placehold.it/470x350\" alt=\"Generic placeholder image\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(11871,1382,'_featurette_c','field_528adda1a27c9'),(11872,1382,'featurette_d','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main-odd\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Blackwood Woodburning Cookstove</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">A loyal companion in the h