 confidence. Set the heat for Low and Slow at 225˚ for 4, 5, or 6 hours and let our smoker do the work. Brisket fans can run the smoker on a single stock of fuel starting at 225˚ and see the temperature at 205˚ - 12 hours later!</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side-odd\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image img-responsive\" src=\"http://placehold.it/470x350\" alt=\"Generic placeholder image\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(13404,1497,'_featurette_b','field_528ad98ffd9e5'),(13405,1497,'featurette_c','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Bake</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">The Thermashell’s natural convection with added radiant reflection produces better airflow and browning than competitive top vented grills.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image img-responsive\" src=\"http://placehold.it/470x350\" alt=\"Generic placeholder image\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(13406,1497,'_featurette_c','field_528adda1a27c9'),(13407,1497,'featurette_d','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main-odd\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Rotisserie</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">The industry exclusive, patent-pending integrated rotisserie option on the Caliber Thermashell Pro™ turns chicken into the family favorite in just over an hour. Crusted to perfection and rockin’ with juicy goodness, experience hands-free roasting while you prepare your side dishes for the poultry feast. Collect cooking juices for basting and sauce creation while keeping your grill clean and flare up free.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side-odd\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image img-responsive\" src=\"http://placehold.it/470x350\" alt=\"Generic placeholder image\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(13408,1497,'_featurette_d','field_528add60a27c7'),(13409,1497,'featurett