opy styled hoods, Vent-A-Hood is your best choice for your island application. Featuring traditional, contemporary, and modern options, you won\'t have to compromise style for performance.'),(14213,1573,'_intro_paragraph','field_528baacf900df'),(14214,1573,'featurette_a','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-7 content-col-main\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Features</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">The Vent-A-Hood Island Magic Blower system is specifically designed to pull and capture grease and smoke from all four sides. Drafts and large open areas are no match for the Magic Lung power.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-5 content-col-side\"><img class=\"featurette-image img-responsive\" src=\"http://placehold.it/470x350\" alt=\"Generic placeholder image\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(14215,1573,'_featurette_a','field_528ad8dffd9e4'),(14216,1573,'featurette_b',''),(14217,1573,'_featurette_b','field_528ad98ffd9e5'),(14218,1573,'featurette_c',''),(14219,1573,'_featurette_c','field_528adda1a27c9'),(14220,1573,'featurette_d',''),(14221,1573,'_featurette_d','field_528add60a27c7'),(14222,1573,'featurette_e',''),(14223,1573,'_featurette_e','field_528ae3c4694fd'),(14224,1573,'featurette_f',''),(14225,1573,'_featurette_f','field_528ae3e0694fe'),(14226,1573,'featurette_g',''),(14227,1573,'_featurette_g','field_528ae3f6694ff'),(14228,1573,'featurette_h',''),(14229,1573,'_featurette_h','field_528ae41e69500'),(14230,1573,'featurette_i',''),(14231,1573,'_featurette_i','field_53a9b6beef676'),(14233,1574,'_hero_image','field_53ae0b0387ffd'),(14234,1574,'intro_paragraph','With a compact design, Vent-A-Hood\'s Under-Cabinet Hoods offer optimum performance for all of our cooking needs. Offering multiple lip and color choices, these hoods are powerful while fitting in seamlessly into your kitchen.'),(14235,1574,'_intro_paragraph','field_528baacf900df'),(14236,1574,'featurette_a','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-7 content-col-main\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">PRH6-K Pro</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">This 6\" tall ultimate replacement hood features our exclusive \"Active Canopy\" technology, which captures cooking vapors from all areas of the canopy. Includes the K Series Blower (sound rating is 7.4 sones at high speed). The hood includes SensaSource, halogen lighting, and top vent/back vent capability. Standard widths are 24\", 30\", 36\", and 42\" wide. This hood is only available in Black, Biscuit, Gunsmoke, White, or Stainless Steel finishes. All Vent-A-Hood products are suitable for use in damp locations (outdoor applications such as a covered patio) when installed in a GFCI protected branch circuit.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-5 content-col-side\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image alignnone\" src=\"http://placehold.it/470x350\" alt=\"Generic placeholder image\" width=\"470\" height=\"350\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(14237,1574,'_featurette_a','field_528ad8dffd9e4'),(14238,1574,'featurette_b','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-7 content-col-main-odd\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">SLH6-K Emerald</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">This 6\" tall ultimate replacement hood features our exclusive \"Active Canopy\" technology, which captures cooking vapors from all areas of the canopy. Includes the K Series Blower (sound rating is 7.4 sones at high speed). The hood includes SensaSource, halogen lighting, and top vent/back vent capability. Standard widths are 24\", 30\", 36\", and 42\" wide. This hood is only available in Black, Biscuit, Gunsmoke, White, or Stainless Steel finishes. All Vent-A-Hood products are suitable for use in damp locations (outdoor applications such as a covered patio) when installed in a GFCI protected branch circuit.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-5 content-col-side-odd\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image alignnone\" src=\"http://placehold.it/470x350\" alt=\"Generic placeholder image\" width=\"470\" height=\"350\" /></div>\r\