o style.'),(14358,1596,'_intro_paragraph','field_528baacf900df'),(14359,1596,'featurette_a','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Designer Range Hoods</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">Vent-A-Hood’s Designer Series combines gorgeous form with great function. You don’t have to sacrifice style to enjoy superior technology. Whether it’s one of their most popular styles or a special-order range hood, they will find the exact style that’s right for you.</p>\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" title=\"Designer Series\" href=\"/product/vent-a-hood/designer/\">View details »</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image alignnone wp-image-852 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/JDH_splash_470x470-e1414702860147.jpg\" alt=\"Vent-A-Hood Designer Series Range Hoods\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(14360,1596,'_featurette_a','field_528ad8dffd9e4'),(14361,1596,'featurette_b','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main-odd\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Island Range Hoods</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">With multiple canopy styled hoods, Vent A Hood is your best choice for your island application. Featuring traditional, contemporary, modern, and glass style choices.</p>\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" title=\"Island Series\" href=\"/product/vent-a-hood/island/\">View details »</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side-odd\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image alignnone wp-image-855 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/PYDH18-EPIH18_470x470-e1414702997245.jpg\" alt=\"Vent-A-Hood Island Series Range Hoods\" width=\"398\" height=\"350\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(14362,1596,'_featurette_b','field_528ad98ffd9e5'),(14363,1596,'featurette_c','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Liner Inserts</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">Vent-A-Hood’s Liner Inserts are mounted inside of decorative wood, plaster, tile or metal hoods. Custom and standard insert options are available.</p>\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" title=\"Linear Insert\" href=\"/product/vent-a-hood/liner-inserts/\">View details »</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image alignnone wp-image-1584 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Vent-A-Hood_Liner_Insert_Stainless-steel.jpg\" alt=\"Vent-A-Hood Liner Insert Stainless-steel\" width=\"470\" height=\"350\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(14364,1596,'_featurette_c','field_528adda1a27c9'),(14365,1596,'featurette_d','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main-odd\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">M Series Range Hoods</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">Vent-A-Hood’s M Series Hoods feature a stainless steel canopy with a baffle filter/blower system that offers high air flow volume in 600 – 1000 CFM options.</p>\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" title=\"M Series\" href=\"/product/vent-a-hood/m-series/\">View details »</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side-odd\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image alignnone wp-image-1585 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Vent-A-Hood-MSeries-Wall-Mount-prh18-m.jpg\" alt=\"Vent-A-Hood M-Series Wall Mount Range hood\" width=\"470\" height=\"350\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(14366,1596,'_featurette_d','field_528add60a27c7'),(14367,1596,'featurette_e','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Under-Cabinet Range Hoods</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">Whether you’re looking to replace your current under-cabinet hood or install a range hood with more power, Vent-A-Hood offers a number of great options. With a compact design, these under-cabinet hoods offer optimum performance for all your cooking needs.</p>\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" title=\"Under Cabinet\" href=\"/product/vent-a-hood/under-cabinet/\">View details »</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image alignnone wp-image-1578 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Vent-A-Hood-Under-Cabinet-Series-Range-Hoods-470x350.jpg\" alt=\"Vent-A-Hood Under-Cabinet Series Range Hoods\" width=\"470\" height=\"350\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(14368,1596,'_featurette_e','field_528ae3c4694fd'),(14369,1596,'featurette_f','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main-odd\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Wall Mount Range Hoods</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">Vent-A-Hood Wall Mount Series Hoods are a go-to for all homeowners looking to combine style and performance.</p>\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" title=\"Wall Mount Series\" href=\"/product/vent-a-hood/wall-mount/\">View details »</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side-odd\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image alignnone wp-image-1583 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Vent-A-Hood_Wall_Mount_Range_Hood_CWEAH6-K-ARS_470x350.jpg\" alt=\"Vent-A-Hood Wall Mount Range Hood\" width=\"470\" height=\"350\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(14370,1596,'_featurette_f','field_528ae3e0694fe'),(14371,1596,'featurette_g','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">The History of Vent-A-Hood</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">As the first manufacturer of home cooking ventilation and range hoods, Vent-A-Hood has developed an excellent reputation throughout the ventilation industry by offering a top quality “in stock” range hood, as well as handmade craftsmanship in their “custom” hood series.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side\">\r\n\r\n [youtuber youtube=\'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HpqD1yjI6HA\']\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>'),(14372,1596,'_featurette_g','field_528ae3f6694ff'),(14373,1596,'featurette_h',''),(14374,1596,'_featurette_h','field_528ae41e69500'),(14375,1596,'featurette_i',''),(14376,1596,'_featurette_i','field_53a9b6beef676'),(14377,1597,'_wp_attached_file','2013/11/Vent-A-Hood_M-Series_Hero.jpg'),(14378,1597,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:1400;s:6:\"height\";i:600;s:4:\"file\";s:37:\"2013/11/Vent-A-Hood_M-Series_Hero.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:3:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:37:\"Vent-A-Hood_M-Series_Hero-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:37:\"Vent-A-Hood_M-Series_Hero-300x128.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:128;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:5:\"large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:38:\"Vent-A-Hood_M-Series_Hero-1024x438.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:1024;s:6:\"height\";i:438;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";i:0;}}'),(14379,1597,'_wp_attachment_image_alt','Vent-A-Hood M-Series'),(14380,1598,'hero_image','1597'),(14381,1598,'_hero_image','field_53ae0b0387ffd'),(14382,1598,'intro_paragraph',''),(14383,1598,'_intro_paragraph','field_528baacf900df'),(14384,1598,'featurette_a','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-7 content-col-main\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Wall Mount CXH18-M</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">Subtle, stainless steel bands and rounded shape of this European wall-mount hood create a unique design. Hood is available in stainless steel. Matching wall mount duct cover (sold separately) is available in standard sizes for 8\', 9\', and 10\' ceiling heights or in custom sizes.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-5 content-c