e','1614'),(14508,1615,'_hero_image','field_53ae0b0387ffd'),(14509,1615,'intro_paragraph','Marvel brings you the widest selection of built-in refrigeration sizes and configurations, including all-refrigerators, all-freezers, refrigerator/freezers, wine cellars and beverage centers. Models are available in 6 inch increments from 18 to 72 inches. Marvel’s full-size integrated solutions are never mass produced, but made just for you with years of experience, craftsmanship, and the highest quality components.'),(14510,1615,'_intro_paragraph','field_528baacf900df'),(14511,1615,'featurette_a','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Side-by-Side</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">Each of MARVEL\'s side-by-side refrigerator/freezers displays our commitment to superior construction, choice and capacity. Interiors are solidly built in your choice of arctic white or gleaming stainless steel. All products are frost-free and have the exclusive MARVEL cooling system for optimum performance. Door options include stainless steel and panel/overlay. The refrigerator door is also available in a glass door with stainless steel wrap or panel/overlay. Only MARVEL offers you an extensive choice of widths. Available in 36”, 42” 48” and our exclusive large capacity 60” and 72” models, these refrigerators are exceptional when it comes to food preservation and are unequalled in terms of capacity. All models have an automatic ice maker, LED interior lighting, clear crispers, easily adjustable interior shelves and formed metal door bins.</p>\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" title=\"Side-by-Side Refrigeration\" href=\"/product/marvel/built-in/side-by-side-refrigeration/\">View details »</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side\"><a href=\"/product/marvel-products/built-in/marvel-side-by-side-ref-470x350/#main\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-932\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image img-responsive wp-image-932\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/marvel-side-by-side-ref-470x350.jpg\" alt=\"Marvel Side by Side Refrigeration\" /></a></div>\r\n</div>'),(14512,1615,'_featurette_a','field_528ad8dffd9e4'),(14513,1615,'featurette_b','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main-odd\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">All Refrigerator Columns</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">These beautiful columns have the largest interior capacity on the market. Finished with either stainless steel or panel/overlay door, our all-refrigerator columns offer you interior choices of arctic white aluminum or gleaming stainless steel. The all-refrigerator is also available with a glass door in two trim options: stainless or panel- ready.</p>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">All refrigerator columns are available in 24\", 30\" and 36\" widths.</p>\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" title=\"All Refrigerator Columns\" href=\"/product/marvel/built-in/all-refrigerator-columns/\">View details »</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side-odd\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image img-responsive\" src=\"http://placehold.it/470x350&amp;text=need+lifestyle+image\" alt=\"Generic placeholder image\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(14514,1615,'_featurette_b','field_528ad98ffd9e5'),(14515,1615,'featurette_c','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">All Freezer Columns</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">Finished with either stainless steel or panel/overlay door, our all- freezer columns offer you interior choices of arctic white aluminum or gleaming stainless steel. The all-freezer features an automatic ice maker.</p>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">All freezer columns are available in 18\", 24\", 30\" and 36\" models.</p>\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" title=\"All Freezer Columns\" href=\"/product/marvel/built-in/all-freezer-columns/\">View details »</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image img-responsive\" src=\"http://placehold.it/470x350&amp;text=need+lifestyle+image\" alt=\"Generic placeholder image\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(14516,1615,'_featurette_c','field_528adda1a27c9'),(14517,1615,'featurette_d','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main-odd\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Wine Storage</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">Your wine collection is a reflection of your good taste, so it is only fitting that such a prize investment be carefully and beautifully preserved. MARVEL offers a selection of undercounter and full-height wine storage refrigerators with up to a 98-bottle capacity. Choose from single or dual-zone wine cellars. Both models feature Marvel’s exclusive cooling system, which keeps each section at optimum temperature.</p>\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" title=\"Wine Storage\" href=\"/product/marvel/built-in/wine-storage/\">View details »</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side-odd\"><a href=\"/product/marvel-products/marvel-undercounter-refrigeration/61wcm704_3barm753-det-470x350/#main\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-889\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image img-responsive wp-image-889\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/61WCM704_3BARM753-DET-470x350.jpg\" alt=\"Marvel Wine Cooler\" /></a></div>\r\n</div>'),(14518,1615,'_featurette_d','field_528add60a27c7'),(14519,1615,'featurette_e','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Top Freezer</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">This popular design, with integral ice maker, is available in three sizes and your interior choice of arctic white or stainless steel. All models have adjustable shelving and storage bins, daylight interior lighting, perforated FreshFlo™ stainless steel shelving, and the exclusive MARVEL cooling system.</p>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">Top freezer models available in 24\", 3