tte\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Islands</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">Create a fully featured outdoor kitchen in no time at all with a premium Sedona Island Package. Available in two color schemes, and offered with a choice of 30” or 36” grills, these Islands also include an outdoor-rated refrigerator, rotisserie, double side burner and a combination storage system with two fully enclosed pull-out drawers. A 15” overhang along the rear of the island accommodates seating and a circular end counter extension adds extra space for entertaining.</p>\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/product/sedona-by-lynx/islands\">View details »</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image alignnone wp-image-1635 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Sedona_Lifestyle_by_Lynx_Island.jpg\" alt=\"Sedona Lifestyle by Lynx Island\" width=\"470\" height=\"350\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(14688,1626,'_featurette_a','field_528ad8dffd9e4'),(14689,1626,'featurette_b','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main-odd\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Freestanding</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">Enjoy the advanced grilling technology and superior craftsmanship of Sedona by Lynx™ in a form that’s at home in any outdoor area—even small patios. Sedona Freestanding models offer a full range of grill sizes and convenience features. And they roll easily on heavy-duty castors, so you can quickly reposition your grill, or store it when you’re not entertaining.</p>\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/product/sedona-by-lynx/freestanding/\">View details »</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side-odd\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image alignnone wp-image-1633 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Sedona_by_Lynx_Freestanding.jpg\" alt=\"Sedona by Lynx Freestanding\" width=\"272\" height=\"350\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(14690,1626,'_featurette_b','field_528ad98ffd9e5'),(14691,1626,'featurette_c','<div class=\"row featurette\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 col-md-7 content-col-main\">\r\n<h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Built-In Grills</h2>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">Sedona by Lynx built-in grills include ProSear™ infrared technology that delivers intense and controllable infrared heat, continuously welded joints to create a superior fit and finish, spark ignition system with battery back-up, control illumination with blue LED lights, specially designed high-density ceramic radiant briquettes, a large and easy-to-read temperature gauge, and stainless steel grilling grates.</p>\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/product/sedona-by-lynx/built-in-grills/\">View details »</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col-md-5 content-col-side\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail featurette-image alignnone wp-image-1634 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Sedona_by_Lynx_Built-in.jpg\" alt=\"Sedona by Lynx Built-in\" width=\"470\" height=\"350\" /></div>\r\n</div>'),(14692,1626,'_featurette_c','field_528adda1a27c9'),(14693,1626,'featurette_d',''),(14754,1635,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:470;s:6:\"height\";i:350;s:4:\"file\";s:43:\"2014/11/Sedona_Lifestyle_by_Lynx_Island.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:2:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:43:\"Sedona_Lifestyle_by_Lynx_Island-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:43:\"Sedona_Lifestyle_by_Lynx_Island-300x223.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:223;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";i:0;}}'),(14694,1626,'_featurette_d','fi