a\" href=\"/product/verona/\">View details »</a></p></div><div class=\"col-sm-3 col-md-3\"><a href=\"/product/verona_italy_218x260/#main\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-1093\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail alignnone wp-image-1093 size-full\" title=\"Verona Appliances\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/verona_italy_218x260.jpg\" alt=\"Verona Appliances\" width=\"218\" height=\"260\" /></a></div></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row featurette\"><div class=\"col-sm-3 col-md-3\"><h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Lynx</h2><p>Build your dream outdoor kitchen with Lynx’s complete line of outdoor kitchen products. Whether you’re designing a custom outdoor kitchen installation, or looking for a ready-made island package, Lynx Professional Grills and Sedona By Lynx has a perfect fit.</p><p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" title=\"Lynx\" href=\"/product/lynx/\">View details »</a></p></div><div class=\"col-sm-3 col-md-3\"><a href=\"/product/crossflame_pro_218x260-2/#main\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-1120\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail  alignnone wp-image-1120 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/crossflame_Pro_218x2601.jpg\" alt=\"crossflame_Pro_218x260\" width=\"218\" height=\"260\" /></a></div><div class=\"col-sm-3 col-md-3\"><h2 class=\"featurette-heading\">Caliber</h2><p>Caliber offers a well-appointed range of products in our outdoor collection including the ultra performance Crossflame Pro™ Grill</p><p><a class=\"btn btn-default btn-primary\" title=\"Caliber\" href=\"/product/caliber/\">View details »</a></p></div><div class=\"col-sm-3 col-md-3\"><a href=\"/product/crossflame_pro_218x260-3/#main\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-1120\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail  alignnone wp-image-1122 size-full\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/crossflame_Pro_218x2602.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"218\" height=\"260\" /></a></div></div>','Products','','inherit','closed','closed','','640-revision-v1','','','2014-10-21 14:59:15','2014-10-21 22:59:15','',640,'/640-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(609,1,'2013-11-19 1